      "content": "Hey, I'm studying for my Con Law exam and I'm a bit stuck on the 2nd Amendment stuff. In your opinion, is the current Supreme Court's interpretation of the Second Amendment actually an accurate reflection of what the Founders intended, or is it more like judicial overreach? I'm trying to figure out which side has the stronger legal footing.",
